casebody.data:
No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado.

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $134,165.44 for the period February 1 through October 15, 2000, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 921.]
